title: Analysis: GOP is party desperately in search of a leader
text: Photo: John Locher, AP Republican presidential candidate Donald Trump speaks at a rally Thursday, Oct. 8, 2015, in Las Vegas. Trump spoke at the Treasure Island hotel and casino on the Las Vegas Strip. Trump says Army Sgt. Bowe Bergdahl should face execution for leaving his post in Afghanistan six years ago and says he is a "no good traitor," and 30 years ago, he would have been shot. Republican presidential candidate Donald Trump speaks at a rally... WASHINGTON (AP) — The GOP is a party in chaos, desperately in search of a leader.
